<h2>New Mentorship Request from {{menteeName}}</h2>

<p>Hello {{mentorName}},</p>

<p>Great news! {{menteeName}} would like you to be their mentor on Spiriment.</p>

<div class='info-box'>
  <p style='margin: 0 0 10px 0;'><strong>From:</strong> {{menteeName}}</p>
  {{#if message}}
    <p style='margin: 10px 0 0 0;'><strong>Personal Message:</strong></p>
    <p style='margin: 5px 0 0 0; padding: 10px; background-color: #f5f5f5; border-left: 3px solid #3A5A40; font-style: italic;'>
      "{{message}}"
    </p>
  {{/if}}
</div>

<p style='text-align: center;'>
  <a href='spiriment://notifications' class='button'>Review Request in App</a>
</p>

<p>You can review this mentorship request and accept or decline it in the Spiriment app. {{menteeName}} is excited to learn and grow in their faith journey with your guidance.</p>

<p style='margin-top: 30px;'>
  <strong>What's Next?</strong><br/>
  • Open the Spiriment app<br/>
  • Go to your Notifications<br/>
  • Review the mentorship request<br/>
  • Accept or decline with a personal message
</p>

<p>If you accept, {{menteeName}} will be able to message you and schedule mentoring sessions with you.</p>

<p>Thank you for your dedication to mentoring and helping others grow in their faith journey.</p>

<p style='margin-top: 30px;'>
  Blessings,<br/>
  <strong style='color: #3A5A40;'>The Spiriment Team</strong>
</p>
